modName: Bathing Beauties or Beefcake - Luxury Suite Remodel to Burning Beauties
summary: Bathing Beauties or Beefcake - Luxury Suite Remodel to Burning Beauties. You need download orginal mod from http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/11427/? and then overwrite with this small file. Instead pool in mid of house is now fire place and benchs to sit around
descriptionHtml:
How to instal :
<br />
<br />1. download and instal mod from http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/11427/?
<br />2. download my remodel and overwrite the file
<br />3. Enjoy warmth : P

File not including npc. you get npc together with main mod from link above. This file is only remodel of house. ( wooden floor with fireplace two benches, white gold rugs from Dragonsreach and 2 pelts on second floor, general cosmetic improvement also some small changes outside : removed flowers and a signboard at front of house ) Think it looks more clean now Luxury - hunt style house with burning beauties.

important : DOESN'T work with other remodel for example A Classier BB Luxury Suite by RIP88. Only on orginal Luxury suite so either classier or this.
author: Hermione2442
